title: Bug 109020In expression builder, when click on "Operaters" button, it is inserted in the head of a row.
description: Description: In expression builder, when click on "Operaters" button, it isinserted in the head of a row.Steps to reproduce:In expression builder, add a column of data set in expression field, thenclick on "+" button, you will find "+" is inserted in front of the data setcolumn.
